description:
The origin of the most devastating diseases in the world can be traced back to man-made disturbances. Just as diseases like cancer, Alzheimer's,  infertility, birth defects and much more have increased with the introduction of and continuous exposure to 2nd,3rd and 4th generation technology, more devastating symptoms and diseases are currently at works with the introduction of 5G.  There are no coincidences.
